race.comment: SALLY CAN WAIT (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (25.28) in a Grade 5 at Sale. Has ability and is a key runner. IRINKA ASHLEY (1) is suited by the inside draw. Last start finished 4th in a Grade 5 on November 13 over 460m at this track behind Wild Cuddle beaten 8 lengths (26.61). Can feature with the right run. DARNUM RAIN (6) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (23.20) at this track. Worth following up. JUMBUK DAMIEN (5) is another with top-three prospects.
